        <div class="bi"><span class="bi-ico">âœˆ</span><div><span class="bi-lbl cs">Altitude: </span><span class="bi-txt">Typically &lt;1,200 ft AGL. Can navigate building corridors, courtyards, and interior spaces.</span></div></div>
        <div class="bi"><span class="bi-ico">ğŸ’¨</span><div><span class="bi-lbl cs">Speed: </span><span class="bi-txt">&lt;100 knots. FPV variants can exceed 80+ mph in sprint â€” difficult to track optically.</span></div></div>
