        <div class="al a-warn"><span class="al-ico">âš </span><span><strong>Airspace Overlap:</strong> Altitude band overlaps with helicopters, low-flying aircraft operating in DC SFRA. Positive identification before kinetic action is non-negotiable.</span></div>
        <div class="al a-orange"><span class="al-ico">ğŸ”¶</span><span><strong>Autonomous Operation:</strong> May fly pre-programmed route with no active RF uplink â€” jamming alone is insufficient. Kinetic options must be pre-authorized.</span></div>
