      <div class="sbb sb-blue">
        <div class="cl">
          <div class="cl-i"><div class="cl-box"></div><span><span class="cl-lbl">Â§130i / Â§124n:</span> Written delegation received from SecDef or SecDHS-designated authority. Know your authority boundaries.</span></div>
          <div class="cl-i"><div class="cl-box"></div><span><span class="cl-lbl">ROE Card:</span> Current ROE/RUF card reviewed, signed, and carried. Know escalation thresholds for Groups 1 and 2 separately.</span></div>
