          <div class="bi"><span class="bi-ico">ğŸ“»</span><div><span class="bi-lbl cn">Frequency Log: </span><span class="bi-txt">Document all frequencies detected during engagement. Pass to SIGINT/TECHINT for operator attribution.</span></div></div>
          <div class="bi"><span class="bi-ico">ğŸ“</span><div><span class="bi-lbl cn">Control Node: </span><span class="bi-txt">If RF bearing obtained during engagement, pass to FBI for ground search of operator location. Time-stamp all bearing data.</span></div></div>
          <div class="bi"><span class="bi-ico">ğŸ”„</span><div><span class="bi-lbl cn">Pattern Update: </span><span class="bi-txt">Update site RF baseline with new signature data. Adjust detection thresholds to improve future detection speed for this threat type.</span></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
