  <!-- Reset & LL -->
  <div class="col">
    <div class="chdr chh-green"><span class="chdr-icon">ğŸ”„</span><div><div class="chdr-title">Reset &amp; Lessons Learned</div><div class="chdr-sub">Restore posture Â· Improve the system</div></div></div>
    <div style="padding:5px 6px;">
      <div class="sb">
        <div class="sbh sbhh-green"><span class="sbh-ico">ğŸ”„</span><span class="sbh-txt">System Reset (2â€“6 Hours)</span></div>
        <div class="sbb sb-green">
          <div class="cl">
            <div class="cl-i"><div class="cl-box"></div><span>All EW systems returned to standby. Frequencies recalibrated post-engagement.</span></div>
            <div class="cl-i"><div class="cl-box"></div><span>Sensor positions reassessed â€” reposition if electronic signature was emitted during engagement.</span></div>
